languages.text: "Может, и не грабил. Значит, знаешь, кто грабил. Или кто товар сбывал. Или кто болтал, что знает, кто сбывал. Ничего, ты у нас в исповедальне покаешься. Все каются".
"Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: “或许你确实没抢过，但你知道是谁抢的，或是谁负责销赃。或者说，你听到过有人自称认识销赃的人。噢，你会在我们的忏悔室中忏悔的，每个人都需要忏悔。”
languages.original_text: "Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: «Puede que no lo hayas hecho... Pero sabes quién ha sido. O quién ha vendido lo que se robó. O quién sabe quién lo ha vendido. Te arrepentirás en nuestro confesionario, igual que todo el mundo».
languages.original_text: "Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: 「お前はしていないかもしれない。だが犯人を知っているだろう。もしくは盗品を売り捌いた張本人を。それか、盗品を売り捌いた奴を知っている者はどうだ。さあ、懺悔室で悔い改めろ。みんなそうするんだ」
languages.original_text: "Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: "Vielleicht nicht. Aber Ihr wisst, wer es war. Oder wer die Ware verkauft hat. Oder wer erzählt hat, er wisse, wer sie verkauft hat. Oh, Ihr werdet bei Eurer Beichte bereuen. Alle bereuen."
languages.original_text: "Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: « Peut-être bien que non. Mais vous connaissez le coupable. Ou celui qui a vendu les marchandises. Ou quelqu'un qui aurait mentionné le connaître. Oh, vous allez vous repentir en salle de confession. Tout le monde se repent. »
languages.original_text: "Maybe you didn't. But you know who did rob it. Or who sold the goods. Or who talked about knowing who sold them. Oh, you'll repent in our confessional. Everyone repents."

languages.text: "Belki soymamışsındır ama kimin soyduğunu biliyorsun. Onu değilse malları kimin sattığını. Kimin sattığını bilen birinden duymuşsundur belki. Herkes gibi sen de tövbe edeceksin."
